                <h1>Housing reform betrays Duke&#039;s diversity</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/b56c7840-58af-4078-8670-570969ea8fff.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
